Keeping with last year’s tradition, this post comes when we are almost 1/5th through this year.
2022 projects Expense Tracker I built a personal Expense Tracker over the month of October using SQLite and Streamlit, because I wasn’t comfortable sharing my financial data with a 3rd party. I’ve tried to keep it simple, so it’s not a pain to use. But, I’ve also tried to keep it extensible, for others to try and use.

